      "writtenOn": "2020-08-04T13:41:19Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I\u0027d prefer to avoid using SkASSERT to catch I/O errors. If an I/O error happened in release we would get an inexplicable, difficult-to-reproduce error with corrupt/truncated shader text.",
